metadata.name: SX001 - Dance of the Druids
metadata.description:
WORLD 001:
The Mystical Forest Lands, home to the great forest spirits of old. Before the age of man and the machine, there was once peace and tranquility. The world was young and green. The Fairies and their little helpers, the Kodama, would keep the trees and creatures healthy, to help them grow and prosper. 

1/1 NFT Artwork
1/1 Physical Signed Print (for initial auction winner)
1 Hires jpg of artwork
Unlockable Content -Seamless Loop MP4 Video & Timelapse of Artwork Creation
